So you need to ADD 
        <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET"/>
to get permission accesing local browser

then make input for user inputing their browse Address .
because default, android cant read the Url . so put this code
  if(!url.startsWith("http://") && !url.startsWith("https://"))
        {
            url = "http://" + url;
        }
        
